content:
...(thinking), {短暂停}
My first reaction was to refuse.
If they tried to take it by force, I would destroy the violin.

Oh, (sizing you up) could it be that you...{短暂停}
Feel sorry about this? Or perhaps you think that
our client would use any means necessary to take it by force anyway.

Or to put it another way,
if you're looking for shortcuts from me,
that's absolutely out of the question.
